  { id: 62, title: "Black Seed Cures Everything: Except Death", slug: "black-seed-cure-hadith", category: "scientific", excerpt: "Muhammad's claim about the miraculous black seed.", readingTime: 9, publishedAt: "2024-03-03", featured: false, status: "published",
    content: `<h2>The Miracle Cure?</h2>

